---++ Datapath for the UIMA Cpe GUI
The CPE Gui has to be told the datapath, as it does not access Eclipse settings.  <br />
This can be done by providing an argument to the _run configuration_ in Eclipse:
   * Add the following snippet to the VM Arguments ="-Duima.datapath=/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_community_mining:/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_core:/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_ir:/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_ml:/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_opinion_mining:/home/herbert/workspace/dkpro_semantics:/home/herbert/workspace/lexsemresource"=
   * Adjust this to *your* path, or it still will not work




